vertices, the vertex separator problem (VSP) is to find a partition of V into three classes A,B and C
such that there is no edge between A and B, max{|A|,|B|}less than or equal β(n), and |C| is
minimum. In this thesis, we consider aninteger programming formulation for this problem. We
